></span>，故 k＞0，<br>△AOB的面积为S=<span  mathtag="math" ><table cellspacing="-1" cellpadding="-1" style="width:auto;display:inline-table;*display:inline;vertical-align:middle;margin:0;padding:0;text-align:center;line-height:normal;" style="display:inline-table;vertical-align:middle"><tr><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black">1</td></tr><tr><td>2</td></tr></table></span>×<span  mathtag="math" ><table cellspacing="-1" cellpadding="-1" style="width:auto;display:inline-table;*display:inline;vertical-align:middle;margin:0;padding:0;text-align:center;line-height:normal;" style="display:inline-table;vertical-align:middle"><tr><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black">2k+1</td></tr><tr><td>k</td></tr></table></span>×（2k+1）=<span  mathtag="math" ><table cellspacing="-1" cellpadding="-1" style="width:auto;display:inline-table;*display:inline;vertical-align:middle;margin:0;padding:0;text-align:center;line-height:normal;" style="display:inline-table;vertical-align:middle"><tr><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black;padding-bottom:1px;font-size:90%">4<span><span>k</span><span style="vertical-align:super;font-size:90%">2</span></span>+4k+1</td></tr><tr><td>2k</td></tr></table></span>=2k+2+<span  mathtag="math" ><table cellspacing="-1" cellpadding="-1" style="width:auto;display:inline-table;*display:inline;vertical-align:middle;margin:0;padding:0;text-align:center;line-height:normal;" style="display:inline-table;vertical-align:middle"><tr><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black">1</td></tr><tr><td>2k</td></tr></table></span>≥4，<br>当且仅当 k=<span  mathtag="math" ><table cellspacing="-1" cellpadding="-1" style="width:auto;display:inline-table;*display:inline;vertical-align:middle;margin:0;padding:0;text-align:center;line-height:normal;" style="display:inline-table;vertical-align:middle"><tr><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black">1</td></tr><tr><td>2</td></tr></table></span>时等号成立，此时面积取最小值4，k=<span  mathtag="math" ><table cellspacing="-1" cellpadding="-1" style="width:auto;display:inline-table;*display:inline;vertical-align:middle;margin:0;padding:0;text-align:center;line-height:normal;" style="display:inline-table;vertical-align:middle"><tr><td style="border-bottom:1px solid black">1</td></tr><tr><td>2</td></tr></table></span>，直线的方程是：x-2y+4=0．<br>（3）由直线过定点（-2，1），可得当斜率 k＞0 或k=0时，直线不经过第四象限．<br>故k的取值范围为[0，+∞）．</TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE>
